---
title: Carb Smart Bunless Pork Burgers with Olive-Tomato Topper and Feta Sauce
description: Explore the gently smoky and sweet flavour of red pepper pesto, which does double duty in this carb conscious recipe. It's used in both the juicy pork patties as well as the tangy vinaigrette that ties the entire meal together.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R1038_W19_CA_RP160777-1_Main_low-5714648c.jpg
